data.description: Stunning 4/2 home in Cypress Woods, packed with modern features and a fantastic layout for comfortable living. The updated kitchen, complete with granite countertops and sleek black stainless appliances, is perfect for cooking and entertaining. It seamlessly flows into a spacious family room for relaxation and gatherings. Additional living areas offer flexibility - use them as formal spaces, a home office, or playroom. The split floor plan ensures privacy in the master suite, featuring an updated bath and walk-in closets.Beautiful wood plank ceramic tile flooring in the main areas, and 9-foot ceilings add an open, elegant feel. Step outside to a large screened porch with tranquil pond views. Brand new roof and a newer A/C (2022).
